{"title":"打仗为了俺","authors":["林十柴"],"dates":[{"year":1948,"month":11,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"打仗为了俺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林十柴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＠过大河翻高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路小路都通太原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵、民工、担架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送公粮的毛驴连成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿湾湾星闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参战的队伍过不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子肩上扛三八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶亮的刺刀真"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耀眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人看了都喝采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人见了心胆寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的公粮驴背上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉手里拿皮鞭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空中皮鞭“叭叭”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不得一步赶到火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"线上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支队伍长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过完一天又一天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支队伍来得远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走的路程快上千。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱是河北顺德府，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱是山西平定县。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱是前年把身翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能不来支援解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个老汉五十三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着毛驴上火线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下看见解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼笑成一条线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上前拉住同志的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自头到尾你拉个遍："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“俺家就住寿阳县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年十月匪军才滚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一头毛驴给拉走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三间房子都烧完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子被抓走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离家一年没有信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又冷又饿没人管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受苦受罪说不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从来了解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受罪的日子俺过完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这回听说打太原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带头参战理当然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓住老阎雪仇恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们父子才得团圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"封建老根要挖掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安生的日子才长远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打完太原打北平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放华北下江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时俺还要参战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉住老蒋才算完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去了全国封建根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安生康乐万万年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺来支援解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军打仗就是为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了咱。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知心话儿没拉完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后面催他把路赶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉说吧着烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起皮鞭往大队里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听皮鞭“叭叭”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着大队人马奔向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太原城。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}